Package com.ibm.streams.management

Interface ApplicationConfiguration

public interface ApplicationConfiguration
ApplicationConfiguration contains information about an application configuration store. An application configuration store provides secure storage and retrieval of name/value pairs.
See Also:
  • DomainMXBean.makeApplicationConfiguration(String, String, Map, String)
